{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Qpdq5rkAv8vFTjPPyfR9Z1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes are complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented across 10 files:\n\n### Changes Summary\n\n**New `harness` field** — Tasks can now use either `\"claude\"` (default) or `\"codex\"` as the execution harness.\n\n| File | Changes |\n|------|---------|\n| `internal/models/task.go` | Added `Harness` field to `Task` and `CreateTaskRequest`; validation rejects values other than `claude`/`codex` |\n| `internal/config/config.go` | Added `DefaultHarness` (`claude`), `DefaultCodexModel` (`gpt-5.4`), and `OpenAIAPIKey` config fields |\n| `internal/store/sqlite.go` | Added `harness` column to schema, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE, and Scan — all at 29 columns |\n| `internal/api/handlers.go` | Harness-aware model defaulting: codex tasks default to `gpt-5.4`, claude tasks to `claude-sonnet-4-6` |\n| `internal/orchestrator/docker.go` | Passes `HARNESS` and `OPENAI_API_KEY` env vars to containers |\n| `docker/Dockerfile` | Installs `@openai/codex` alongside `@anthropic-ai/claude-code` |\n| `docker/entrypoint.sh` | Branched CLI invocation: `claude` runs Claude Code CLI, `codex` runs Codex CLI with `--approval-mode full-auto` and `--reasoning-effort`; harness-aware auth validation and output parsing |\n| `scripts/create-task.sh` | Added `--harness` option and included it in JSON payload |\n| `internal/models/task_test.go` | Added test cases for valid/invalid harness values |\n| `internal/store/sqlite_test.go` | Added `Harness` field to test task and assertion for round-trip |\n| `internal/api/handlers_test.go` | Added `DefaultHarness`, `DefaultCodexModel`, `DefaultEffort` to test config |\n\n### Key design decisions:\n- **Default harness**: `claude` (backward compatible)\n- **Codex defaults**: model `gpt-5.4`, effort `high`\n- **Codex auth**: requires `OPENAI_API_KEY` env var (independent of `AUTH_MODE`)\n- **Codex CLI flags**: `--model`, `--reasoning-effort`, `--approval-mode full-auto`, `--quiet`"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":522,"cache_read_input_tokens":90700,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":522,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2af19d51-84dc-4ce3-80b2-7d4b83aa4cbe","uuid":"4e9f6b07-37ef-46d7-a2d6-60029b5ada65"}
